ABOUT ME

I made this blog for 80's babies who grew up in a time before the internet. For the generation that grew up on YO! MTV Raps and Rap City. For all those who copped The Purple Tape on cassette. For those whose first video game console was the original NES.



In addition, this blog is for movies buffs. For those who watched their favorite movies from a VCR. Who were there opening night for the latest blockbuster. Who grew up on Siskel & Ebert film reviews. Who spent many Friday nights perusing the selections in Blockbuster Video.

CATEGORIES
  • Film
  • Music
  • Sports
